<ab facs="#facs_448_r1l23">fürbraht wie Jn dıeſelb Jr habe noch niht wider worden ſey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_448_r1l24"><expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> . daʒ Jr den <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Jr habe </ab>
