<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Hans, als wir euch nehst
                                                  <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von der habe und
                                                kauffmanschaft wegen, so ir
                                                  <add><expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan></add> Friczen
                                                  <expan>Schoszharte<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>Elspete<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>sein<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>wirtin<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>Heincze<ex>n</ex></expan> Herbst und
                                                  <expan>Gerhawse<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>sein<ex>er</ex></expan> wirtin, aufgehalten
                                                habt, <add>also</add> sind die
                                                  <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>wirtin<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> aber bede
                                                  <add>für</add> uns
                                                  <add><expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan></add> und
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns fürbraht, wie in
                                                dieselb ir habe noch niht wider worden sey.
                                                  <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir den
                                                  <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ir habe und
                                                kauffmanschaft noch
                                                  <expan>widergeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                                                  <expan>ungehind<ex>er</ex>t</expan> vollgen lassen
                                                wöllet <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>. Als etc. Das
                                                  <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.
                                                  <add>Antwurtt</add>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> iii
                                                  <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Urbani.</ab>
</div>
